data.description: WELCOME HOME! This gorgeous one-story home was built by DR Horton just 2 years ago. It features 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and 2 car garage. The foyer opens to the guest bedrooms, bath and hall linen closet. Center kitchen includes breakfast bar with beautiful quartz counter tops, stainless steel appliances and corner pantry and opens to a large family room. The primary suite features a sloped ceiling and attractive primary bath with dual vanities, water closet and spacious walk-in closet. The standard rear covered patio is located off the dining area.
